# Research docs (local only). `research/*` (not `research/`) so the negations
# below can re-include specific subtrees — git can't descend into a dir that's
# already excluded by `research/`.
research/*
# ...except the Maestro prompt artifacts — they're shipped with the bundle
# (tsup copies them to dist/prompts/) and need to be in git for CI.
!research/prompts/
